ARMSTRONG
v.
UC LENDING CORP. No. 499P06-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2007. Patricia Duffy, Assistant Attorney General, for UC Lending Corp.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 9th day of February 2007 by Plaintiff for "Petition for Rehearing":
